## Evidence Status Legend

- `confirmed`: Dynamically verified issue.
- `triaged_active_candidate`: Candidate retained after model-assisted triage.
- `static_candidate`: Static candidate without dynamic proof.
- `unreachable_candidate`: Static candidate not reachable from entry points.
- `suppressed`: Finding suppressed by policy/risk acceptance.

